      • discreteFrechet

        public static double discreteFrechet(ILineString p,
                                     ILineString q)
        Discrete Fréchet distance.

        Complexity O(pq).

        Eiter, Thomas; Mannila, Heikki (1994), Computing discrete Fréchet distance, Tech. Report CD-TR 94/64, Christian Doppler Laboratory for Expert Systems, TU Vienna, Austria.

        Parameters:
        p - linestring
        q - linestring
        Returns:
        the discrete Fréchet distance between the 2 input polygonal curves

      • discreteFrechetWithProjection

        public static double discreteFrechetWithProjection(ILineString p,
                                                   ILineString q)
        Discrete Fréchet distance. This method reproject the points from each curve to the other (only to the closest projection). This still has to be tested.

        Complexity O(pq).

        Eiter, Thomas; Mannila, Heikki (1994), Computing discrete Fréchet distance, Tech. Report CD-TR 94/64, Christian Doppler Laboratory for Expert Systems, TU Vienna, Austria.

        Parameters:
        p - linestring
        q - linestring
        Returns:
        the discrete Fréchet distance between the 2 input polygonal curves
